Package frogger.model.selfMovable

Class SelfMovable

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.Node
      • javafx.scene.image.ImageView
        • frogger.model.Movable
          • frogger.model.selfMovable.SelfMovable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.css.Styleable, javafx.event.EventTarget
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Car, End, Log, Turtle, WetTurtle
    public abstract class SelfMovable
extends Movable

    SelfMovable

    A SelfMovable is a Movable which can move itself.

    This class extends SelfMovable.

    This class can set up a element in game with action, position and image.

    Since:
    0.1
